head_commit.message:
App Exclusions Revamp - VPN-3892 & friends (#6016)

* VPN-3892 && VPN-2953: Revamp app exclusions

* Update string call

* Clean up

* Update objectName

* Fix some test flakiness maybe

* Fix typo

* Move success toast to main.qml

* Review changes

* Update VPNSimplePopUp buttons

* Post-UX review changes

* Add tutorial_04_split_tunneling3 and update tests

* Add Accessible.name to exclusion checkboxes.

* Add max client version to tutorial_04_split_tunneling2

* Actually resetAppPermissions.js
